docs {
  # List Chats
  
  Get list of all chat windows (tmux) for a project.
  
  ## Query Parameters
  - `projectPath` (string): Absolute path to the project
  - `projectId` (string): Alternative: Base64-encoded project path
  
  ## Response
  ```json
  {
    "chats": [
      {
        "id": "tmux-mobile-project:1",
        "terminalId": "tmux-mobile-project:1",
        "windowName": "chat-claude-auth-bug",
        "tool": "claude",
        "topic": "auth-bug",
        "sessionName": "mobile-project",
        "windowIndex": 1,
        "type": "chat",
        "active": true
      }
    ],
    "total": 1
  }
  ```
}
